<HEADLINE>
<P>
YOUTH CAMP DONATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A $500 grant has been made to the Hawthorne Parks and Recreation Foundation by 
the Hawthorne Municipal Employees Assn. The money is earmarked for the Richard 
F. Huhn Fund, a special fund set aside for the eventual construction of a new 
