<P>
Photo, Winning style -- Race to the finish line Thursday at Hollywood Park, 
above, heats up. JOE KENNEDY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, After jockey Laffit 
Pincay, below, who had been leading the pack, was thrown by his horse, Bruho. 
The $111,500 On Trust Handicap purse went to Stylish Winner, ridden by Robbie 
Davis. (See story, charts in Sports.) 
</P>
